{"tid":1978004,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港監獄義士: 寄語獄外手足","createTime":"2020-04-18T11:17:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T03:37:42.000Z","uid":134071,"like":84,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"86e13455ffb02b14492096c58ee2956155b3298d","tid":1978004,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T11:17:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/shumlester/photos/a.101447961346859/152343839590604/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshumlester%2Fphotos%2Fa.101447961346859%2F152343839590604%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=TvWZhBC8jRU6oyAzZT7RDnWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=755f2323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/shumlester/photos/a.101447961346859/152343839590604/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n岑敖暉<br />\n22 小時 &middot;<br />\n<br />\n【牆內手足之寄語】<br />\n<br />\n今天去探監，知道「黃色批鬥圈」之事已在牆內傳得廣為人知，當牆內眾人都為抗爭、為各位而憂心時，只能說我們實在要好自為之。<br />\n<br />\n全文如下：<br />\n<br />\n諸牆外手足、諸同路香港人，別來無恙。憶起上一封致諸位之公開信，已係昨年之事。至今數月，全港甚至全球形勢皆日益嚴峻。縱我等牆內手足僅能藉報紙電視電台等有限途徑一窺世情，亦無減半分對當今事態之擔憂，故復上書一函告之。<br />\n<br />\n近月正值抗疫之際，本為全民大事。奈何港共軍政府非但未有恤民予息，反逆其道而行，秋後算帳之外，更乘時重推廿三條，更有甚者圖用反恐條例、借反恐之名或清算或囚柙所有民主自由抗爭者，使香港新疆化，再無天日。<br />\n<br />\n身陷囹圄，可做之事無多。祈無復有手足被捕被告之外，惟望尚於牆外之眾多位，可戒危慎難，莫大意失僅餘寸土！或曰：法治已死，或曰：雖不中亦不遠。誠然如此，毋阻抗爭。若對比二惡法放之任之，後患無窮。故然，今已蒙難之或軍火或爆炸品之干犯者首當其衝，於其後，旋即成全港自由人之夢魘，定要忌之防之。<br />\n<br />\n為所有或被捕或遭受酷刑或被姦或被拐或遇害者，<br />\n共勉之。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/3kQUetB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3kQUetB.jpg&h=ba057b37&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"029cb5562c294eb6deb9a9db7cf4dc52ef18f69d","tid":1978004,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T11:17:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0db146951750c74ed4b57765fb48d27e09ce6b4","tid":1978004,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T11:18:52.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3f289f0f98edb937f0f456421be1768b41f6e2f","tid":1978004,"uid":258578,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T11:19:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8ee05e1fdc9cdeb34d79809fcb15970b84e48d20","tid":1978004,"uid":312125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T11:20:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f661ed59a0928ebaa4b423644bc52aa731b8d323","tid":1978004,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T11:20:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80c19e8693cce1f5f0dce53ddb8b700296f58380","tid":1978004,"uid":245065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T11:20:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"47c2cfb22313a0d3cd7a32990716f100ac15f40d","tid":1978004,"uid":253978,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T11:21:13.000Z","msg":"多謝你地嘅付出<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地會回歸正常生活嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99fa598b7ab05db547a433eed32b5642904761a2","tid":1978004,"uid":205927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T11:21:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家生性"},{"pid":"c2da7e30813df8a6e7e5ec27430b0915915f4460","tid":1978004,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T11:21:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\